      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MONUMENT (2) missed the frame last time, finishing 4th (30.13) last time in a Grade 5 at Sandown. Has never been out of the money this course and distance including one win. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Key runner on his best form. LAKEVIEW LEIGH (1) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 24.91 beating Mackenzie Rose. Should be in this for a long way. MARSHAL LEE ROSE (8) had been in super honest form hitting the frame two times on end before finishing seventh (30.34) at Sandown last time. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. STOMPER ROMPER (7) is new to this track but not to be underestimated.",
